{"type":"click","text":"A\n    \n      Indicator Dashboard + Signal Table\n      Top strip: Auto-computed indicator pills (Macro regime, Market type, Day type, Orderflow signals) — all visible, no gates. Color-coded green/yellow/red.\n      Middle: Multi-timeframe VP levels bar — session POC/VAH/VAL, weekly composite, leg profile, macro profile. Shows where current price sits relative to each VP anchor. User can input custom level anchors (leg start date, macro start date).\n      Bottom: Signal table always visible (no gating). Each signal row shows its score + which indicators confirm it.\n      Like ValuePage: FilterBar at top, signals always shown, indicators inline per row.","choice":"a","id":null,"timestamp":1773409092026}
